    "After a thorough review of the literature, we could not find any similar article dealing with the addressed topics in our contribution.",
    "Specifically, there exists vast literature dealing with the generation and detection of deepfakes.",
    "Therefore, our goal in this regard is to provide main insights for the reader to quickly delve into the topic.",
